---
description: Frontend guidance for Next.js admin console
globs:
  - "**/apps/web/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Preserve routing, metadata, and loading/error states.
- Do not break accessibility basics.
- Avoid large client-side state unless justified.
- Prioritize information density and operational clarity over visual flair.
- Pages should help operators answer: which agent acted, what was attempted, what was approved, what evidence was recorded.
